## Key Insights
- Rust uses HMAC-SHA256(auth_hash, jwt_secret) for server-side storage — port with `crypto.createHmac`
- JWT: access token 15min, refresh token 7d, HS256, claims: `{sub, iat, exp, tokenType}`
