### 7. Production Deploy Steps (CentOS 7/9)

1. Install Node.js 22 LTS via nvm or nodesource
2. Install PM2 globally: `npm i -g pm2`
3. Install MongoDB 7 (or use Docker)
4. Clone repo, `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`
